label: uncl6353
comment: Code qualifying the type of unit.

values.label: Number of pricing units
values.comment: Number of units which multiplied by the unit price gives price.

values.label: Transportable unit
values.comment: A unit that is capable of being transported.

values.label: Number of debit units
values.comment: The number of units which are debited by the sender of the consignment to the receiving party.

values.label: Number of received units
values.comment: The number of units which are received by the receiving party of the consignment.

values.label: Number of free days for container availability
values.comment: Number of days within which the container will be made available at no charge.

values.label: Number of structure components
values.comment: Number of components in a structure.

values.label: Number of asset units
values.comment: The number of units of an asset.

values.label: Number of trial balance accounts
values.comment: The unit is trial balance account.

values.label: Senior citizen
values.comment: The unit is a senior citizen.
